\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Real-world validation under moderate perturbation (inject rate = 0.2). Without protection, 62\% of upstream failures propagate to final failure. Both AI-based and adaptive circuit breakers eliminate cascade failures (CFR = 0.0). The AI-based circuit breaker achieves the highest end-to-end success rate in this setting.}}{5}{figure.2}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:real}{{2}{5}{Real-world validation under moderate perturbation (inject rate = 0.2). Without protection, 62\% of upstream failures propagate to final failure. Both AI-based and adaptive circuit breakers eliminate cascade failures (CFR = 0.0). The AI-based circuit breaker achieves the highest end-to-end success rate in this setting}{figure.2}{}}
