\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces Containment--intervention tradeoff. While both circuit breaker variants eliminate cascade failures, adaptive policies trigger more frequently, resulting in lower end-to-end success compared to the static AI-based breaker. This highlights the challenge of designing efficient adaptive control mechanisms.}}{6}{figure.3}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:tradeoff}{{3}{6}{Containment--intervention tradeoff. While both circuit breaker variants eliminate cascade failures, adaptive policies trigger more frequently, resulting in lower end-to-end success compared to the static AI-based breaker. This highlights the challenge of designing efficient adaptive control mechanisms}{figure.3}{}}
